                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_provincialPriorityResultsRepeater_ctl00_ResultItem1';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Brampton/Ontario/5_30774591_ON20071022111213670/?ursrc=ppl&showcpo=ShowCPO';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl12_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Bowmanville/Ontario/5_31026884_20120322144856875/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=13_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");

                        }

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl15_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Mississauga/Ontario/5_31023262_ON20070723102323353/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=16_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl16_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Mississauga/Ontario/5_31022699_ON20080116103533937/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=17_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl18_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Vaughan/Ontario/5_31022413_ON20080207101646875/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=19_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl19_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Vaughan/Ontario/5_31021618_ON20080207101646875/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=20_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl20_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Vaughan/Ontario/5_31021595_ON20080207101646875/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=21_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl23_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Vaughan/Ontario/5_31021484_ON20080207101646875/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=24_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),

                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));

                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl26_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Scarborough/Ontario/5_31021469_ON20080130104719054/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=27_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });

                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl28_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Vaughan/Ontario/5_31021309_ON20080207101646875/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=29_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl29_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Vaughan/Ontario/5_31020908_ON20080207101646875/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=30_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();

                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Mississauga/Ontario/5_31019328_ON20071205111337842/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=37_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl47_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Caledonia/Ontario/5_31009408_ON20080204112819796/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=48_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl54_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic+Sedan/Newmarket/Ontario/5_31008794_ON20071205103351061/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=55_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl55_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic+Sedan/Brampton/Ontario/5_31008409_ON20080213110815117/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=56_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl58_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Milton/Ontario/5_31007193_ON20090715110843576/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=59_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl66_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Thornhill/Ontario/5_31002178_ON20090112102238078/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=67_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl70_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Toronto/Ontario/5_30995226_ON20080130105033148/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=71_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();

                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Toronto/Ontario/5_30994665_ON20080611094525059/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=75_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");

                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");

                            results = regex.exec(url);

                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl76_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Toronto/Ontario/5_30992252_ON20080130105033148/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=77_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl77_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = true;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Toronto/Ontario/5_30991267_ON20080103120602351/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=78_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl78_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = true;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Toronto/Ontario/5_30991208_ON20080103120602351/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=79_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl86_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Pickering/Ontario/5_30981577_ON20081124094103812/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=87_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>
            
    
	</div>
   
    </div>

                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl88_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Toronto/Ontario/5_30980818_ON20080611094525059/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=89_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl90_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Toronto/Ontario/5_30978888_ON20080611094525059/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=91_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
                </script>

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl93_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Hamilton/Ontario/5_30977355_ON20080421102317203/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=94_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl94_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = true;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Hamilton/Ontario/5_30977347_ON20080421102317203/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=95_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    
                    function getParameterByName(name, url) {
                        if (!url) url = window.location.href;
                        name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
                        var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                            results = regex.exec(url);
                        if (!results) return null;
                        if (!results[2]) return '';
                        return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        var adResultItemParameters = new aew.AdResultItemParameters();
                        adResultItemParameters.adResultItemClientID = 'ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_MainContent_normalResultsRepeater_ctl96_ResultItem2';
                        adResultItemParameters.hideCarouselImageButton = false;
                        adResultItemParameters.detailPageURL = 'http://www.autotrader.ca/a/Honda/Civic/Toronto/Ontario/5_30968392_ON20080130105033148/?ursrc=hl&showcpo=ShowCPO&orup=97_100_807';

                        var adResultItem = new aew.AdResultItem(adResultItemParameters);

                        var numberOfAds = $( "div[data-list-numerical-position]" ).length;
                        var desiredAdPosition = 3;
                        var notFirstPage = getParameterByName("rcs");

                        if (notFirstPage == "") {
                            if (numberOfAds >= desiredAdPosition) {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+desiredAdPosition+"]" ).before("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            } else {
                                $("div[data-list-numerical-position="+numberOfAds+"]" ).after("<div id='fsk_splitbox'></div>");
                            }
                        }

                    });
